  <span class="target" id="ecommerce-platform-x-cart"></span><div class="section" id="x-cart-store-integration">
<h1>X-Cart Store Integration<a class="headerlink" href="#x-cart-store-integration" title="Permalink to this headline">Â¶</a></h1>
<ol class="arabic">
<li><p class="first">Download the <a class="reference external" href="https://www.talkable.com/xcart/curebit.zip">X-Cart Curebit Module</a> and unzip it to your X-Cart main directory.</p>
</li>
<li><p class="first">Open the file located at:</p>
<div class="line-block">
<div class="line"><em>/skin/%FOLDER WITH YOUR CURRENT SKIN%/customer/main/order_message.tpl</em></div>
</div>
<p>using your favorite text editor if you use an external skin, otherwise edit:</p>
<div class="line-block">
<div class="line"><em>/skin/common_files/customer/main/order_message.tpl</em></div>
</div>
</li>
<li><p class="first">Add the following code at the end of the file:</p>
<div class="code highlight-python"><div class="highlight"><pre><span></span>{if $active_modules.Curebit}{include file=&quot;modules/Curebit/curebit.tpl&quot;}{/if}
</pre></div>
</div>
</li>
<li><p class="first">Save this file and upload it to your site.</p>
</li>
<li><p class="first">Run the script located at <em>http://www.yoursite.com/curebit_install.php</em></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p><br></p>
<p><a class="reference internal" href="../verify.html#ecommerce-verify"><em>Verifying Integration Instructions</em></a></p>
